# ERP Backoffice — Project Overview

## Monorepo layout (pnpm workspaces)

```
apps/
  api/             NestJS backend (port 4000)
  backoffice-web/  React admin SPA (port 3000)
  pos-web/         React POS SPA (port 3001)
packages/
  ui/              @erp/ui — shared component library (shadcn/ui pattern)
  api-client/      @erp/api-client — generated OpenAPI TypeScript client
  shared-interfaces/ @erp/shared-interfaces — shared TypeScript types
  shared-kafka-client/ @erp/shared-kafka-client — Kafka/Redpanda wrapper
```

## Commands

```bash
pnpm install            # install all workspaces
make dev-api            # start NestJS API
make dev-backoffice     # start backoffice at :3000
make dev-pos            # start POS at :3001
pnpm openapi:generate   # regenerate @erp/api-client from running API
pnpm migration:run      # run TypeORM migrations
pnpm seed:inventory     # seed demo data
```

## Stack

- **Frontend**: React 19, TypeScript 5, Vite 6, React Router v7, TanStack Query v5, Zustand v5
- **UI**: Tailwind CSS 3 + Radix UI primitives (via `@erp/ui`)
- **Backend**: NestJS 11, TypeORM, PostgreSQL, Redis, Redpanda (Kafka-compatible)
- **Language**: Vietnamese UI labels throughout

## Multi-tenant model

Every operational record scoped by `organizationId` (company) + `branchId` (branch).
- JWT payload: `{ userId, organizationId, roles[], branchIds[], jti }`
- Active branch passed via `X-Branch-Id` header
- `@Actor` param decorator in controllers resolves the active actor context

## Key conventions

- IDs are UUID v4
- Monetary values: `NUMERIC(18,2)` in DB
- All timestamps stored in UTC
- Vietnamese labels in UI (`label: "Tên hàng hóa"`)
- `synchronize: false` — all schema changes via TypeORM migrations
- Business transactions (stock ledger, journals) are immutable after posting
